===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|tr|ota|یمك|tr=yemek|gloss=food, meal}}. Cognate to {{cog|qwm||tr=yemek|t=food|sc=Arab}}, ultimately derived from {{der|tr|trk-pro|*jē-||to eat}}, see etymology 1 above.
====Noun====
{{tr-noun|yemeği|ler}}
# [[meal]], [[food]]
# [[repast]]
# [[dish]], particular kind of food
